Package: hyperestraier
Version: 1.4.10
Revision: 2
Description: Full-text search system
License: LGPL
Homepage: http://hyperestraier.sourceforge.net/
Maintainer: PHO <phonohawk@ps.sakura.ne.jp>

Source: mirror:sourceforge:%n/%n-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: cf4ca3dea77d161517388050654b52a6

Depends: <<
  %N-shlibs (>= %v-%r)
<<

BuildDepends: <<
  qdbm14,
  libiconv-dev
<<

ConfigureParams: --libexecdir=%p/lib/%n --mandir=%p/share/man --enable-stable --enable-zlib --disable-lzo --disable-bzip

CompileScript: <<
  ./configure %c
  make mac
<<

InstallScript: <<
  make install-mac DESTDIR=%d
<<

SplitOff: <<
  Package: %N-shlibs
  Files: lib/libestraier.*.dylib
  Shlibs: %p/lib/libestraier.8.dylib 8.0.0 %n (>= 1.4.10-1)
  DocFiles: COPYING ChangeLog README THANKS
  Depends: qdbm14-shlibs, libiconv
<<

SplitOff2: <<
  Package: %N-dev
  BuildDependsOnly: True
  Depends: %N-shlibs
  Files: include/*.h lib/libestraier.a lib/libestraier.dylib lib/pkgconfig/*.pc
  DocFiles: COPYING ChangeLog README THANKS
<<

DocFiles: COPYING ChangeLog README THANKS

DescDetail: <<
Hyper Estraier is a full-text search system. You can search lots of
documents for some documents including specified words. If you run a
web site, it is useful as your own search engine for pages in your
site. Also, it is useful as search utilities of mail boxes and file
servers.

Note that estseek.cgi and other CGIs are located on
%p/lib/%n/ instead of %p/libexec
<<
